questionText:
What will this program print?

```c
int x = 5;
if (x = 0) {
    printf("True");
} else {
    printf("False");
}
```

What will this program print?

```c
int a = 10, b = 20;
printf("%s", (a > b) ? "A greater" : "B greater");
```

What will happen if the user enters 0 in this code?

```c
int num;
scanf("%d", &num);
if (num) {
    printf("Non-zero");
} else {
    printf("Zero");
}
```
